\b\fs28 16. Support And Maintenance\b0\fs20\par
Support for SakayoriMusic is provided on a best effort basis through community channels, including the GitHub issue tracker, the GitHub discussion forum, and the community Discord server. No service level agreement, response time guarantee, or priority support offering is available. Sakayori Studio may discontinue support for older versions of the software at its discretion, typically by encouraging users to upgrade to a current version through the in-app update mechanism.\par
